hh3cTransceiver.name: hh3cTransceiver

revisions.description: Add hh3cTransceiverChannelTable to transceiver channel statistics.

Add the objects of hh3cTransceiverTempHiAlarm, hh3cTransceiverTempLoAlarm, hh3cTransceiverTempHiWarn, hh3cTransceiverTempLoWarn, hh3cTransceiverVccHiAlarm, hh3cTransceiverVccLoAlarm, hh3cTransceiverVccHiWarn, hh3cTransceiverVccLoWarn, hh3cTransceiverBiasHiAlarm, hh3cTransceiverBiasLoAlarm, hh3cTransceiverBiasHiWarn, hh3cTransceiverBiasLoWarn, hh3cTransceiverPwrOutHiAlarm, hh3cTransceiverPwrOutLoAlarm, hh3cTransceiverPwrOutHiWarn, hh3cTransceiverPwrOutLoWarn, hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrHiAlarm, hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrLoAlarm, hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrHiWarn, hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrLoWarn, hh3cTransceiverErrors.

Add the objects of hh3cTransceiverDiagnostic, hh3cTransceiverCurTXPower, hh3cTransceiverMaxTXPower, hh3cTransceiverMinTXPower, hh3cTransceiverCurRXPower, hh3cTransceiverMaxRXPower, hh3cTransceiverMinRXPower, hh3cTransceiverTemperature, hh3cTransceiverVoltage, hh3cTransceiverBiasCurrent.
The initial revision of this MIB module.

hh3cTransceiver.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Technologies Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cTransceiver.description: The objects in this MIB module are used to display the information of transceiver on interface.

hh3cTransceiverInfoTable.name: hh3cTransceiverInfoTable
hh3cTransceiverInfoTable.description: This table shows transceiver information on an interface.

hh3cTransceiverHardwareType.name: hh3cTransceiverHardwareType
hh3cTransceiverHardwareType.description: Hardware type of the interface, such as SM(single mode).

hh3cTransceiverType.name: hh3cTransceiverType
hh3cTransceiverType.description: Type of the interface, such as SFP/XFP/GBIC.

hh3cTransceiverWaveLength.name: hh3cTransceiverWaveLength
hh3cTransceiverWaveLength.description: Wave length of the interface, measured in nanometer.

hh3cTransceiverFiberDiameterType.name: hh3cTransceiverFiberDiameterType
hh3cTransceiverFiberDiameterType.description: The diameter of the fiber, measured in micron. fiber9 - 9 micron multi-mode fiber fiber50 - 50 micron multi-mode fiber fiber625 - 62.5 micron multi-mode fiber copper - copper cable.

hh3cTransceiverTransferDistance.name: hh3cTransceiverTransferDistance
hh3cTransceiverTransferDistance.description: The maximum distance which the interface can transmit, measured in meter.

hh3cTransceiverDiagnostic.name: hh3cTransceiverDiagnostic
hh3cTransceiverDiagnostic.description: Indicating the digital diagnostic monitoring function.

hh3cTransceiverCurTXPower.name: hh3cTransceiverCurTXPower
hh3cTransceiverCurTXPower.description: Indicating the current transmitted power. The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

hh3cTransceiverMaxTXPower.name: hh3cTransceiverMaxTXPower
hh3cTransceiverMaxTXPower.description: Indicating the maximum transmitted power. The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

hh3cTransceiverMinTXPower.name: hh3cTransceiverMinTXPower
hh3cTransceiverMinTXPower.description: Indicating the minimum transmitted power. The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

hh3cTransceiverCurRXPower.name: hh3cTransceiverCurRXPower
hh3cTransceiverCurRXPower.description: Indicating the current received power. The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

hh3cTransceiverMaxRXPower.name: hh3cTransceiverMaxRXPower
hh3cTransceiverMaxRXPower.description: Indicating the maximum received power. The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

hh3cTransceiverMinRXPower.name: hh3cTransceiverMinRXPower
hh3cTransceiverMinRXPower.description: Indicating the minimum received power. The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

hh3cTransceiverTemperature.name: hh3cTransceiverTemperature
hh3cTransceiverTemperature.description: Indicating the current temperature. The unit is Celsius centigrade.

hh3cTransceiverVoltage.name: hh3cTransceiverVoltage
hh3cTransceiverVoltage.description: Indicating the current voltage. The unit is in hundredths of V

hh3cTransceiverBiasCurrent.name: hh3cTransceiverBiasCurrent
hh3cTransceiverBiasCurrent.description: Indicating the current bias electric current. The unit is in hundredths of mA

hh3cTransceiverTempHiAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverTempHiAlarm
hh3cTransceiverTempHiAlarm.description: Transceiver temperature high alarm threshold limit in thousandths of degrees Celsius. As an example: 49120 is 49.120 degrees Celsius.

hh3cTransceiverTempLoAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverTempLoAlarm
hh3cTransceiverTempLoAlarm.description: Transceiver temperature low alarm threshold limit in thousandths of degrees Celsius. As an example: 49120 is 49.120 degrees Celsius.

hh3cTransceiverTempHiWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverTempHiWarn
hh3cTransceiverTempHiWarn.description: Transceiver temperature high warning threshold limit in thousandths of degrees Celsius. As an example: 49120 is 49.120 degrees Celsius.

hh3cTransceiverTempLoWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverTempLoWarn
hh3cTransceiverTempLoWarn.description: Transceiver temperature low warning threshold limit in thousandths of degrees Celsius. As an example: 49120 is 49.120 degrees Celsius.

hh3cTransceiverVccHiAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverVccHiAlarm
hh3cTransceiverVccHiAlarm.description: Transceiver VCC high alarm threshold limit in hundreds of microvolts. As an example: 32928 is 3.2928 volts. Returns zero if not supported on the transceiver.

hh3cTransceiverVccLoAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverVccLoAlarm
hh3cTransceiverVccLoAlarm.description: Transceiver VCC low alarm threshold limit in hundreds of microvolts. As an example: 32928 is 3.2928 volts. Returns zero if not supported on the transceiver.

hh3cTransceiverVccHiWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverVccHiWarn
hh3cTransceiverVccHiWarn.description: Transceiver VCC high warning threshold limit in hundreds of microvolts. As an example: 32928 is 3.2928 volts. Returns zero if not supported on the transceiver.

hh3cTransceiverVccLoWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverVccLoWarn
hh3cTransceiverVccLoWarn.description: Transceiver VCC low warning threshold limit in hundreds of microvolts. As an example: 32928 is 3.2928 volts. Returns zero if not supported on the transceiver.

hh3cTransceiverBiasHiAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverBiasHiAlarm
hh3cTransceiverBiasHiAlarm.description: Transceiver bias high alarm threshold limit in microamps.

hh3cTransceiverBiasLoAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverBiasLoAlarm
hh3cTransceiverBiasLoAlarm.description: Transceiver bias low alarm threshold limit in microamps.

hh3cTransceiverBiasHiWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverBiasHiWarn
hh3cTransceiverBiasHiWarn.description: Transceiver bias high warning threshold limit in microamps.

hh3cTransceiverBiasLoWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverBiasLoWarn
hh3cTransceiverBiasLoWarn.description: Transceiver bias low warning threshold limit in microamps.

hh3cTransceiverPwrOutHiAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverPwrOutHiAlarm
hh3cTransceiverPwrOutHiAlarm.description: Transceiver transmit power high alarm threshold limit in tenths of microwatts. As an example: 10000 is 1 milliwatt.

hh3cTransceiverPwrOutLoAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverPwrOutLoAlarm
hh3cTransceiverPwrOutLoAlarm.description: Transceiver transmit power low alarm threshold limit in tenths of microwatts. As an example: 10000 is 1 milliwatt.

hh3cTransceiverPwrOutHiWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverPwrOutHiWarn
hh3cTransceiverPwrOutHiWarn.description: Transceiver transmit power high warning threshold limit in tenths of microwatts As an example: 10000 is 1 milliwatt.

hh3cTransceiverPwrOutLoWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverPwrOutLoWarn
hh3cTransceiverPwrOutLoWarn.description: Transceiver transmit power low warning threshold limit in tenths of microwatts. As an example: 10000 is 1 milliwatt.

hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrHiAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrHiAlarm
hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrHiAlarm.description: Transceiver receive power high alarm threshold limit in tenths of microwatts. As an example: 10000 is 1 milliwatt.

hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrLoAlarm.name: hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrLoAlarm
hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrLoAlarm.description: Transceiver receive power low alarm threshold limit in tenths of microwatts. As an example: 10000 is 1 milliwatt.

hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrHiWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrHiWarn
hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrHiWarn.description: Transceiver receive power high warning threshold limit in tenths of microwatts. As an example: 10000 is 1 milliwatt.

hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrLoWarn.name: hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrLoWarn
hh3cTransceiverRcvPwrLoWarn.description: Transceiver receive power low warning threshold limit in tenths of microwatts. As an example: 10000 is 1 milliwatt.

hh3cTransceiverErrors.name: hh3cTransceiverErrors
hh3cTransceiverErrors.description: Bitmask indicating transceiver errors. Transceiver information I/O error(0) Transceiver information checksum error(1) Transceiver type and port configuration mismatch(2) Transceiver type not supported by port hardware(3) WIS local fault(4) Receive optical power fault(5) PMA/PMD receiver local fault(6) PCS receive local fault(7) PHY XS receive local fault(8) Laser bias current fault(9) Laser temperature fault(10) Laser output power fault(11) TX fault(12) PMA/PMD transmitter local fault(13) PCS transmit local fault(14) PHY XS Transmit Local Fault(15) RX loss of signal(16) Unused(17-31)

hh3cTransceiverChannelTable.name: hh3cTransceiverChannelTable
hh3cTransceiverChannelTable.description: This table provides statistics about transceiver with multi-channel.

hh3cTransceiverChannelIndex.name: hh3cTransceiverChannelIndex
hh3cTransceiverChannelIndex.description: The channel index of transceiver. Indicating one channel of the interface.

hh3cTransceiverChannelCurTXPower.description: Indicating the current transmission power. The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

hh3cTransceiverChannelCurRXPower.name: hh3cTransceiverChannelCurRXPower
hh3cTransceiverChannelCurRXPower.description: Indicating the current received power. The unit is in hundredths of dBM.

hh3cTransceiverChannelTemperature.name: hh3cTransceiverChannelTemperature
hh3cTransceiverChannelTemperature.description: Indicating the current temperature. The unit is Celsius centigrade.

hh3cTransceiverChannelBiasCurrent.name: hh3cTransceiverChannelBiasCurrent
hh3cTransceiverChannelBiasCurrent.description: Indicating the current bias electric current. The unit is in hundredths of mA.
